19:27.660 --> 19:31.604
It says, he, the Messiah, will crush your head, Satan.

19:32.405 --> 19:32.725
Okay?

19:33.005 --> 19:43.515
And that is the kingdom program that the Messiah is going to crush and destroy the power and the authority of the devil over mankind.

19:43.575 --> 19:46.578
He's going to crush the enemy.

19:46.946 --> 19:47.567
praise God.

19:48.168 --> 19:57.620
And there's also a prediction of the salvation program because it says, and you, Satan, the serpent, you will bruise his heel.

19:58.321 --> 20:14.802
So you can see what happened at the cross, that serpent, he will crush the serpent on the foot, but at the same time the serpent will bite the heel of the Messiah and inject the poison of sin

20:15.298 --> 20:22.086
