20:22.786 --> 20:23.988
He bore our sins.

20:24.428 --> 20:27.331
He took the curse for our sins, praise God.

20:27.752 --> 20:30.795
He paid the price for our sins and rose from the dead.

20:30.815 --> 20:38.163
So this is a picture of salvation that He would take the poison of the serpent on Himself to set us free from it.

20:38.524 --> 20:40.466
But at the same time, He would

20:40.610 --> 20:52.303
crush him underfoot and in his resurrection he defeated and triumphed over all the powers of the enemy and now he has all authority in heaven and earth, hallelujah.

