22:57.527 --> 23:03.675
So as the greatest son of David, Jesus is the one who is greater than Solomon.

23:04.837 --> 23:08.722
Jesus is both the greater than Isaac and the greater

23:09.122 --> 23:09.823
than Solomon.

23:09.843 --> 23:18.032
These are the two pictures of the suffering Messiah who sacrificed himself for us in.

23:19.053 --> 23:28.043
